abstract: Texas Rangers defeat Tampa Bay Rays, 8-6, to tie American League division series, 1-1.
snippet: Trailing by 3-0, Texas’s offense finally awakened and scored five runs in the fourth inning en route to an 8-6 victory that tied the series at one victory apiece.
lead_paragraph: Trailing by 3-0, Texas’s offense finally awakened and scored five runs in the fourth inning en route to an 8-6 victory that tied the series at one victory apiece.
